"{\"uid\": \"cbsnews.com-news-surfing-caroline-marks-paris-olympic-gold-tahiti\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Watch CBS News  Updated on:  August 9, 2024 / 5:36 PM EDT/ CBS News  Surfer Caroline Marks, 22, is among the star-studded athletes who took home gold during the2024 Paris Olympic Games, adding another medal toTeam USA's growing shelf.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9964888423771276, \"rank\": 0.003523529283387868, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}, {\"begin\": 76, \"end\": 90, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Marks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\"}, {\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9990351508452071, \"rank\": 0.0006055694296840566, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The goofy-footed rider joined CBS News on Friday to share more onher win.\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9964888423771276, \"rank\": 0.003523529283387868, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After four days of riding the Olympic high, she's still processing what she calls the \\\"biggest moment of my career.\\\"\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels so surreal,\\\" she told CBS News.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9964888423771276, \"rank\": 0.003523529283387868, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just trying to feel all of the emotions but I do not know if it's fully soaked in yet.\\\"\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marks' gold medal win upholds Team USA's dominance in the sport of Olympic surfing, which debuted for the first time just three years ago at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.99072133418302, \"rank\": 0.007801831654535088, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American Carissa Moore, who also competed this year, won the inaugural gold medal in 2021.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9984004249263312, \"rank\": 0.0016006664178917344, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carissa Moore\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tahiti presented a fresh opportunity for Marks to showcase her beloved sport on the biggest world stage.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999986185105619, \"rank\": 8.124563877546345e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like it's gotten so much more attention this year than Tokyo, which was really cool to see,\\\" said Marks.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9289831804402096, \"rank\": 0.07644404077356012, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was an honor to be a part of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ten thousand miles from the French mainland, the small island's powerful and unpredictable waves made for an eventful showdown, with awhale even making a surprise appearance at one point.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9986554148669365, \"rank\": 0.0013463954763823175, \"text\": \"French mainland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marks competed against contenders from over a dozen other countries during the five-day event, sheltering at a one-of-a-kind floating Olympic village during off hours.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the gold medal match-up, the Florida native narrowly beat Tatiana Weston-Webb of Brazil by a margin of .17 points.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9999996117072286, \"rank\": 3.472012667036838e-07, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}, {\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatiana_Weston-Webb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tatiana Weston-Webb\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatiana_Weston-Webb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatiana_Weston-Webb\"}, {\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9560917220773386, \"rank\": 0.03171558587251047, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She celebrated her win on social media, posting a picture of her wearing her medal and a wide grin with the caption:\\\"Dreams come true \\ud83e\\udd47 \\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83c\\uddf8 all glory to God.\\\"\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the men's side, Kauli Vaast, a French Polynesian native,out-surfed Australia's Jack Robinson to capture the coveted gold medal.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.4272265630165537, \"rank\": 0.6929850685063254, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.4272265630165537, \"rank\": 0.6929850685063254, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1753, \"end\": 1763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9944441609598078, \"rank\": 0.00501971426831668, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 1782, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9749058236782367, \"rank\": 0.025203521795155254, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.8891439554631735, \"rank\": 0.12264435083088458, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}, {\"begin\": 1799, \"end\": 1807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"score\": 0.7069423304387131, \"rank\": 0.39212476709691213, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next summer Olympic Games in 2028 will unfold in the surfer-friendly waters of Los Angeles, California.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9997723322404488, \"rank\": 0.000222708967031857, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until then, Marks is keeping plenty busy.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the coming days, she plans to travel back to Paris for the closing ceremony, and then make a quick pit stop at home before jetting off for another surfing excursion, this time in Fiji.\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2043, \"end\": 2048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999761258, \"rank\": 2.3923251472259486e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji\", \"score\": 0.9977084906892054, \"rank\": 0.0014505184716888538, \"text\": \"Fiji\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to my next competition and then hopefully competing for the world title in September,\\\" she told CBS News.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9964888423771276, \"rank\": 0.003523529283387868, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So the work's not done yet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2024 CBS Interactive Inc. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2340, \"end\": 2360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS Interactive Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(02:44)  Copyright \\u00a92025 CBS Interactive Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": []}]}"